/* MARK: - Keyboard Setup */
"Setup Progress" = "設定進度";
"Open Cutling Settings" = "開啟 Cutling 設定";
"Tap here, then switch to Cutling" = "在此點選，然後切換至 Cutling";
"How to Use Your Keyboard" = "鍵盤使用方法";
"Storage Limits" = "儲存限制";
"You're All Set!" = "設定完成！";
"Set Up Your Keyboard" = "設定鍵盤";
"Your Cutling keyboard is ready! While typing anywhere, tap the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to switch to Cutling." = "Cutling 鍵盤已準備就緒！在任何地方輸入時，點選鍵盤上的🌐地球圖示切換至 Cutling。";
"Follow the two simple steps below to start using your custom keyboard. This page will automatically update as you complete each step." = "按照以下兩個簡單步驟開始使用您的自訂鍵盤。完成每個步驟後，此頁面將自動更新。";
"**Step 1:** Tap 'Open Cutling Settings' below, go to **Keyboards** and select **Cutling** from the list." = "**第1步：** 點選下方「開啟 Cutling 設定」，進入**鍵盤**，從清單中選擇 **Cutling**。";
"**Step 2:** Make sure **Allow Full Access** is ON. This lets the keyboard copy images to your clipboard. Your data stays private and is never sent anywhere." = "**第2步：** 確認**允許完整存取**已開啟。這將允許鍵盤將圖片複製到剪貼板。您的資料始終保持私密，不會傳送至任何地方。";
"**Step 3:** Tap on the text input and choose \"Cutling\" using the 🌐 globe icon on your keyboard to update the \"Full Access\" status." = "**第3步：** 點選文字輸入框，使用鍵盤上的🌐地球圖示選擇「Cutling」，以更新「完整存取」狀態。";
"**Step 4:** You're good to go! The usage guide is provided below." = "**第4步：** 一切就緒！使用指南在下方提供。";
"While typing in any app, tap or hold the 🌐 globe key at the bottom-left of your keyboard, then select Cutling" = "在任何應用程式中輸入時，點選或長按鍵盤左下角的🌐地球鍵，然後選擇 Cutling";
"Tap any text cutling and it will be typed into your current text field immediately" = "點選任意文字剪切片段，它將立即輸入到目前的文字框中";
"Tap an image cutling to copy it to your clipboard, then paste it into the app you're using (usually by tapping and holding, then selecting Paste). Apple currently does not support directly pasting an image on this app." = "點選圖片剪切片段可將其複製到剪貼板，然後貼到您正在使用的應用程式中（通常是長按後選擇貼上）。Apple 目前不支援在此應用程式中直接貼上圖片。";
"Copy any text, then tap the 'Add from Clipboard' button in the Cutling keyboard to save it as a new cutling" = "複製任意文字，然後在 Cutling 鍵盤中點選「從剪貼板新增」按鈕，即可儲存為新的剪切片段";
"You can manage all your cutlings in the main Cutling app. Changes you make will instantly appear in your keyboard." = "您可以在主要 Cutling 應用程式中管理所有剪切片段。您的更改將立即反映在鍵盤中。";
"Keyboard extensions have strict memory limits to ensure system stability. Images use more memory than text, so we limit them to ensure your keyboard stays fast and reliable. If you reach a limit, simply delete some cutlings to add new ones." = "鍵盤擴充功能有嚴格的記憶體限制以確保系統穩定性。圖片比文字佔用更多記憶體，因此我們限制了數量以保持鍵盤快速可靠。達到限制時，只需刪除一些剪切片段即可新增新的。";
"Up to **%lld text** cutlings" = "最多 **%lld 個文字**剪切片段";
"Up to **%lld image** cutlings" = "最多 **%lld 個圖片**剪切片段";
